# Privacy Policy

For an improved user experience, we require you to sign in with google to access certain features.

We keep just a few pieces of information:
- Email address
- Name
- Google ID (Unique number linked to your account)
- URL to Google Profile picture
- Recipe Likes
- SpicyChef Shopping Cart items

We do not know, and will never request your password or any personal information beyond the listed items above.

Login and Account data is managed by google. All other application data is stored on private servers in norway.

We do not keep access logs directly linked to your account. 

We will delete your account and all associated data if you request it.

We reserve the right to change this policy at any time. If we do, we will post the changes here.

# Terms of Service

Your account and all your data can be deleted at any time, without notice. 

We do not guarantee that the application will be available at all times, or that it will be free of bugs or errors.

You use the application at your own risk. We are not responsible for any damages caused by the application.

The content of the application is provided as is, and we do not guarantee that it is accurate or up to date.

We reserve the right to change the terms of service at any time, without notice.

